Message-ID: <1209B9C5-B7CC-4B80-A108-45D204A05398@roswellpark.org>

Hi,

We allow only one maintainer per package. Please take a look at the instructions at this link, http://bioconductor.org/developers/package-guidelines/#description.

Both you and your colleague can remain an authors but you should remove one of the names as maintainer.

For this reason you do not have an account on BiocCredentials. I can make an account for you on BiocCredentials giving you access to the Bioconductor Git repository. 

I will send a private email with you account information.

Best,

Nitesh 



