hom.At.inp.db
hom.Ce.inp.db
hom.Dm.inp.db
hom.Dr.inp.db
hom.Hs.inp.db
hom.Mm.inp.db
hom.Rn.inp.db
hom.Sc.inp.db
KEGG.db (use KEGGREST instead)


Unresponsive/not-maintained packages:

Software:

SELEX
